{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21023.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story13","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"都雏乃","nameRight":"沙耶香","textLeft":"你说知道谁是犯人了……@真的吗！？沙耶香！","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"当然是真的！@我全都想明白了！"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"那么，@犯人到底是谁！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"textRight":"没错……犯人是……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"咽口水。"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"textRight":"犯人是……"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"犯人是……？"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"是这个！@这颗棒球！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300301}],"textLeft":"哎？"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"你会做出这样的反应也很正常。@可这就是事实……！"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"textRight":"犯人是这颗棒球，@是这个打到了雏乃。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"什么意思……？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":1}],"textRight":"你看，浮现出的脚印中，@有一个圆形痕迹，对吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"这个大小，以及这个接缝，@就是棒球！"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"textRight":"在雏乃倒下的地方@有这颗棒球的痕迹！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"而且它还滚着滚着@跑到了房间的角落。"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"但是为什么会有棒球？"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":0}],"textRight":"棒球社正在运动场上练习呢，@此时此刻也能听见小孩子们的声音。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"而且这个房间……@正好直面运动场！"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"也就是说孩子打出的棒球@偶然从窗户飞进来了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"结果正中@雏乃的后脑勺！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"原来是这样啊！@所以没有犯人的身影。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300301}],"textLeft":"但是……犯人真的是这颗球吗……？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":801300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"那、那个……对不起！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"诶？"},{"chara":[{"id":801300}],"textRight":"刚才有一颗球@飞进这个房间了……"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"球给你，下次要小心哦。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":801300}],"textRight":"好的，谢谢你！再见！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801300}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"沙耶香","textRight":"哎呀真成熟啊，@明明两个人外表都是小学生呢。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:300301:effect_emotion_angry_0][se:7219_strain]嗯？@你刚才说什么？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"不，我什么都没说！@[chara:200401:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:200401:cheek_0][chara:200401:face_mtn_ex_041.exp.json][chara:200401:lipSynch_1]啊哈哈……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"总而言之！事件就此解决了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"棒球吗……这是个盲点……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":1}],"textRight":"啊哈哈哈，还好不是魔女。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"那么，我差不多该回去了。"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"textRight":"我计划去买明天穿的衣服。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"买衣服……是要约会吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":400}],"textRight":"[chara:200401:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]诶！？嗯！？@不不是那样的！"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"太好懂了吧！@[chara:300301:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:300301:cheek_0][chara:300301:face_mtn_ex_000.exp.json][chara:300301:lipSynch_1]好，既然如此。"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"为了感谢你帮我解决事件，@我送你一份小礼物！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"textRight":"礼物？"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"其实我为今天的实验@准备了好几种香料。"},{"chara":[{"id":300301}],"textLeft":"将这个和这个调和在一起……@就能做出一种市面上买不到的香水啦。"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"锵锵！@怎么样？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200401}],"textRight":"这是什么……好香啊！"},{"chara":[{"id":300301}],"textLeft":"是我特制的香水！@当然了，对人体完全无害。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"给你，只要喷上这个，@准能把男孩子迷得神魂颠倒！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"真的吗！谢谢你！@我会珍惜这瓶香水的！"},{"chara":[{"id":300301,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"嗯！约会要加油哦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"textRight":"都说了不是约会……[chara:200401:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:200401:cheek_2][chara:200401:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json][chara:200401:lipSynch_1]哎，算啦！@再见啦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"嗯，祝你好运！"},{"nameNarration":"沙耶香","narration":"通过助人为乐，@收获了一份出乎意料的幸运。","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21023.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"得到了超级芬芳的香水！@接下来要去街上买衣服啦！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200401,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2004_00_03","textHome":"交给魔法侦探沙耶香！有问题都来问我吧！"}],"nameCenter":"沙耶香","textCenter":"一切交给我魔法侦探沙耶香吧！@什么事情都可以询问我！","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200401,"motion":1}]},{"chara":[{"id":200401}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}